Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.00,Memory,,0,0,0,,Fujiwarano Sai, a Go player from the Heian period...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:08.50,Memory,,0,0,0,,has passed through time and returned to\Nthe world in the mind of Shindou Hikaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.70,Memory,,0,0,0,,in order to obtain the Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You won?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! My first victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to see if I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NHe completely ignored you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you guys rivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:18.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He said he'd never appear before\Nme again... he's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's waiting for me to rise up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.89,Background,,0,0,0,,Look this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Change of plans, I'll crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.76,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(330,115)}The Twenty-Fourth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.76,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Ouza vs Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.72,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\iclip(394,345,438,490)\fs30\bord1\fscy103\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\move(424,801,424,-210)}T\Nh\Ne\N|\ND\Ne\Np\Nt\Nh\N|\No\Nf\N|\NS\Np\Ni\Nr\Ni\Nt\Nu\Na\Nl\N|\NW\No\Nn\Nd\Ne\Nr
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:26.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,I envy them... They're going\Nto go watch Touya's match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.00,Sai,,0,0,0,,We played Touya four times to the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we've never seen him play anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And his opponent is the Ouza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I wanna watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.43,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! Hikaru! I'll play just this game for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:44.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll finish it in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Waya! Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiba-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Isumi-kun, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll place the game from move one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll place white.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira draws a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you would pass the pro\Nexams next year, Isumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san is stronger than I\Nam. I just passed out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Mashiba-san's gloating over how he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck is part of your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiba-kun might be the first\Nperson to defeat Touya Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, but none of you will\Nbe able to defeat Touya Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Zama-sensei is struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Look! Zama-sensei used a double-Hane here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the way an Ouza would\Nplay against a mere new pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:03.72,Background,,0,0,0,,A title holder should just connect here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei intends to win no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, let's replay the game over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.14,Background,,0,0,0,,But Touya-kun's playing really well on the black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei's probably biting\Nthe tip of his fan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That habit Zama-sensei has when he's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.61,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There! End game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:37.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hikaru you won by 2\Nand a half moku! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I lost my focus half way through\Nbecause of Touya's match, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,20... 40... 50... 58!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I'm two and a half short. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Right here, did I respond incorrectly?\NShindou-kun, you seemed to move in really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on! Let's go watch\NTouya's match! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... you played well there,\Nbut it can get difficult depending\Non how your opponent responds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.40,Sai,,0,0,0,,Are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to discuss the game!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:20.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Teacher, you don't go over the game with us every\Ntime! Why do you have to choose a time like this to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:29.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I'll... I'll make sure Hikaru reviews the\Ngame once we get home, so please make it short!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He tossed it in! That's really aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:07:04.61,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Zama can cut a point in Touya's formation at\Nthis point, so Touya should have connected there to\Nplay it safe. Instead Touya's threatening to capture the\Nstones that are threatening him. It's a very risky move.]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.75,Note,,0,0,45,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Touya tosses his stone in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.75,Note,,0,0,312,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Biting the fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Black's throw in is a strong move\Nthat won't let White relax at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Everything depends upon white's response to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:43.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}If white cuts, the battle will be very complex. Black\Nwill be in danger, but white will be in danger too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:45.11,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: {\1c&H00FF00&}X {\1c&HDDDDDD&}marks where white can cut black's formation]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:45.11,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H00FF00&\bord3\fs45\pos(352,205)}X
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He captured instead of cutting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,White cowered out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the Ouza avoided a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If white had cut, this, and this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... both white and black are in danger but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei probably avoided\Nbattle out of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No he didn't. He thought he shouldn't cross\Na faulty bridge against a mere new pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.84,Background,,0,0,0,,He's hesitating over Touya Akira's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei must be really bitter over\Nthat. He didn't just pull back, he's\Ncoming into action in a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But will he have a chance to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Black's in the lead! Protect your territory\Nand run towards the goal Akira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. The Ouza won't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't defend just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll move onward still!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}A Kifu of this match will remain.\NShindou will probably see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:41.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Each of my moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not defending the lower\Nside!? You're going to keep fighting!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he's going to leave a weakness\Nin his own territory right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya's well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And he still attacks. Is Touya that type of guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Zama-sensei will attack\Nhim through that weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei's thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Touya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another observer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou! Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya... Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, we'll replay the game for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.75,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya is black and the Ouza is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:52.97,Background,,0,0,0,,There's a handicap, not only does he\Ngo first, black also gets 5.5 moku komi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a handi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between a top pro and a new\Nfirst dan. Of course you'll need a\Nhandicap to make it a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is actually not enough for the new first\Ndan, but the top pro doesn't play seriously,\Nso it turns out to be a close match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Touya's got an easy win?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Ouza is playing seriously today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Using all his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.16,Background,,0,0,0,,But Touya's winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:24.20,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah! White responds by taking\Ninstead of cutting to black's throw in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.54,Background,,0,0,0,,The Ouza is playing carefully!\NAgainst a new first dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing patiently, not rushing the\Ngame, protecting his weaknesses, and\Nwaiting for his opponent to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And take the win for himself in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Zama-sensei is playing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Touya played here, instead of protecting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't protect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more interesting...\Nbut if white comes in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.90,Background,,0,0,0,,Ouza just went in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Black should be well aware that white will\Nmove into where Black's control is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.13,Background,,0,0,0,,How will you fight Touya Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you fight Zama-Ouza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya... you really are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can win if you just protected... but you still\Nattack... what's pushing Akira-kun like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I know... Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,you're telling me to come all this way right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll walk forward, headed towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I will... I'll definitely catch up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:25.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,Even after a thousand years\Nhas passed, it is all still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.90,Sai,,0,0,0,,snow... and the fierce wars on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.58,Sai,,0,0,0,,Each move speaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,of the heart of the ones placing the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:45.70,Sai,,0,0,0,,Now, the sound of the stones, is\Nresounding through that stinging air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.65,Memory,,0,0,0,,Come after me with his skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:14.40,Memory,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll move forward, to a\Nplace that he can never reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't let him come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who chases after me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What I see is the 500 pro players.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And just forward! I'll just move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't even turn to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd respond here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You planned on coming here after that move right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a young one studying under the Touya family,\Nhe probably would've responded there by impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who do you think is\Nsitting before you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's even.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was caught off guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That last move made the winner uncertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:34.30,Background,,0,0,0,,That's Zama sensei... I would've\Nresponded there on impulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:36.93,Background,,0,0,0,,It's already in the end game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.30,Background,,0,0,0,,This is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.40,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the match end with the victor uncertain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya won't let it end here, with the\Nway he's been playing up to now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If they enter the last round\Neven, he'll try to go for a KO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Black, that's too far. He'll get cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You went in too deep Akira-kun! You\Nhaven't read through Ouza's responses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.22,Background,,0,0,0,,He resigned....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the post game discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he was defeated, that was\Na very good game by Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Yes. He did well in chasing the Ouza back that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:04.09,Background,,0,0,0,,Shall we say to Zama-sensei "Good job"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san... wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably won't tell us to get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya. We're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya got defeated trying to go for a KO...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so he loses to people other than Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... won't forget his match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes. Touya's play today was worth watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.03,Background,,0,0,0,,Wow! The snow is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya's going to keep moving forward right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Man he's really worth chasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:56.22,Sai,,0,0,0,,But, Hikaru you've come a long way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's all thanks to Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep chasing after Touya, maybe I'll be\Nable to become Meijin or anything I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:14.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Touya Akira probably would have kept walking his\Nown path without stopping if he hadn't met Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}He stops and turns back, and pulls Hikaru along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}The existence of Touya Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}was placed here by God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}to make Hikaru grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:12.32,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord3\1c&H0E00DC&\3c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\pos(172,355)}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.32,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord3\1c&H0E00DC&\3c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\pos(298,355)}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(471,355)}Igo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(247.625,171.25)}Umezawa Yukari's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's study "Geta" today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H1D7CFA&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(333,201)}Teacher Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&HF40001&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(114,274)}Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&HFF22F7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(495,255)}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H008F04&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,336)}Today:     {\1c&H1200EE&}[Geta]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a good way to\Ncapture this single white stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.53,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H018E08&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,334)}What's a good way to capture this white stone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it Yuuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup you captured it. Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:29.94,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&HFE0016&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,322)}Yuuki is correct!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:35.56,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: This is called a "net" in English]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We call moving here and preventing\Nyour opponent from moving out "Geta".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:35.03,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H2108F5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,291)}[Geta] {\1c&H038B06&}is a method of stopping\Nyour opponent's ability to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai-chan, how about this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:39.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H038A0C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,321)}What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you captured the stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:51.46,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&HFA00F1&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,321)}Mai is correct!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Geta" appears in matches a\Nlot, so let's all remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&HFB2AAF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,351)}Let's remember "Geta"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H1300ED&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\i1\pos(320,321)}To be continued...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rise up to first class right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.62,0:23:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the Wakajishisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.91,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I can't say "To defeat Touya Akira" anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:12.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru you are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:26.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,My moves that cut into you on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:36.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord2\shad1)}Elite-Fansubs presents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:36.60,Memory,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs45\bord2.5\shad1}Hikaru no Go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.71,Op1Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\kf20}君{\kf45}が{\kf106}今{\kf23}{\kf25}僕{\kf31}を{\kf56}支え{\kf65}て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:20.71,Op1Kanji,,0,0,0,,{\kf22}僕{\kf42}が{\kf118}今{\kf14}{\kf24}君{\kf32}を{\kf43}支{\kf78}える
